# Coroot CE Lab on OpenShift 4.18

Validated lab for Coroot CE on OpenShift 4.18.x using Coroot Operator and a pinned custom node-agent.

---

## Validated Environment

* OpenShift: 4.18.38
* Coroot Operator Helm Chart: `coroot-operator-0.9.4`
* Coroot Operator App Version: `1.9.3`
* Custom Node Agent: `ghcr.io/coroot/coroot-node-agent:1.28.3`

---

## Known Issue

The node-agent deployed by the Coroot Operator may fail on OCP 4.18 due to eBPF/verifier incompatibility.

### Workaround

1. Install Coroot Operator
2. Create Coroot CR
3. Disable operator-managed node-agent
4. Deploy custom node-agent `1.28.3`

---

## Repository Structure

```text
coroot-ocp418-lab/
├── README.md
├── coroot/
│   ├── 00-namespace.yaml
│   ├── 01-coroot-cr.yaml
│   ├── 02-disable-operator-node-agent-patch.yaml
│   ├── 03-node-agent-custom.yaml
│   └── 04-coroot-route.yaml
│
├── traffic-demo/
│   ├── 00-traffic-demo.yaml
│   ├── 01-traffic-generator.yaml
│   ├── 02-traffic-demo-advanced.yaml
│   └── 03-traffic-generator-advanced.yaml
│
└── boutique/
    ├── 00-namespace.yaml
    ├── 01-anyuid-scc.sh
    └── 02-frontend-route.yaml
```

---

## Install Coroot Operator

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/00-namespace.yaml

helm repo add coroot https://coroot.github.io/helm-charts
helm repo update

helm install coroot-operator coroot/coroot-operator -n coroot
```

---

## Create Coroot Instance

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/01-coroot-cr.yaml
```

Validate:

```bash
oc get pods -n coroot -w
```

---

## Disable Operator Node Agent

```bash
oc patch ds coroot-node-agent \
  -n coroot \
  --type=merge \
  --patch-file coroot/02-disable-operator-node-agent-patch.yaml
```

---

## Deploy Custom Node Agent

```bash
oc adm policy add-scc-to-user privileged \
  -z coroot-node-agent-custom \
  -n coroot

oc apply -f coroot/03-node-agent-custom.yaml
```

---

## Expose Coroot UI

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/04-coroot-route.yaml
```

Get Route:

```bash
oc get route coroot -n coroot
```

Login:

```text
Username: admin
Password: CorootAdmin123!
```

---

## Deploy Simple Traffic Demo

```bash
oc apply -f traffic-demo/00-traffic-demo.yaml
oc apply -f traffic-demo/01-traffic-generator.yaml
```

---

## Deploy Advanced Traffic Demo

```bash
oc apply -f traffic-demo/02-traffic-demo-advanced.yaml
oc apply -f traffic-demo/03-traffic-generator-advanced.yaml
```

---

## Deploy Online Boutique Demo

```bash
oc apply -f boutique/00-namespace.yaml

oc apply -n boutique -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/microservices-demo/main/release/kubernetes-manifests.yaml

bash boutique/01-anyuid-scc.sh

oc rollout restart deploy -n boutique

oc apply -f boutique/02-frontend-route.yaml
```

Get Boutique Route:

```bash
oc get route boutique-frontend -n boutique
```

---

## Validation

Check Node Agent Health:

```bash
oc logs -n coroot \
  -l app.kubernetes.io/component=coroot-node-agent-custom \
  --tail=30
```

Expected:

```text
metrics remote write endpoint: http://coroot-coroot.coroot:8080/v1/metrics
sent metrics in XXms
```

